precis:
Acceptance of an Instrument (REVOCATION OF TIMBER SURRENDER) wherein the
LYACKSON BAND revokes a 1941 and a 1944 marketable timber surrender
affecting the whole of Lyackson Indian Reserve No. 3 and Shingle Point
Indian Reserve No. 4, in British Columbia.
